    thinking: "**Building Key Views**\n\nI\'ve made excellent progress; the community feed is visually stunning and really captures the right atmosphere. Now, I\'m shifting focus to the crucial views, beginning with the ScheduleView component. I\'ve completed the searchable schedule, and I\'m integrating the favorites calendar state and note-taking functionality. The SongsView is next on my list.\n\n\n**Constructing Detailed Agenda**\n\nI\'m focused on the ScheduleView now, and it\'s taking shape quite nicely. The core structure is becoming robust. I\'ve got the day selection tabs, category chips for filtering, and the text search working smoothly. The collapsible detailed agenda cards are also coming together, including the \"Star Session\" toggle linked to localStorage for personalized timetables. I\'m especially excited about integrating the \"My Journal/Notes\" text box for each session; the instant save feature is really going to make it a great tool. I\'m starting work on the campus map now, too.\n\n\n"
