    thinking: "**Constructing Core Components**\n\nI\'m now focused on the two remaining key components: `SongsView.tsx` which will handle the song list with its search function, lyric tabs, and audio helper, and `MapView.tsx`, which handles the directions planner and local places directory.\n\n\n**Designing SongsView.tsx**\n\nI\'m currently designing `/src/components/SongsView.tsx`. I\'ve outlined key features like a fast keyword-indexed search, horizontal category filters, dual-view lyrics (English/Malayalam transliteration), accessibility controls (font magnification), and a Liturgical Synth Helper for practice melodies using the Web Audio API. This will include a \"Practice Melody\" button that triggers a client-side synthesizer for melodies, like the \"Theme G-Chant\".\n\n\n"
