    modified_response: "I will configure and augment the application with **Progressive Web App (PWA)** capabilities, rendering it installable on any Android device as a standalone application. \n\nHere is my 3-step design plan to make this a full-fledged installable PWA for Android:\n1. **PWA Manifest Configuration**: Create a high-fidelity `manifest.webmanifest` defining application name, start parameters, background colors, secure orientation constraints, and display configuration (`standalone` mode to hide the browser URL bar like a native APK).\n2. **Launch & Touch Compatibility**: Add mobile theme colors, apple/android touch icons, dynamic address bar customizations, and touch targets to `index.html`.\n3. **PWA Registrations**: Setup lightweight background service workers for caching assets/hymns so it functions offline or in low-connectivity areas on mobile devices.\n\nLet\'s implement this now!"
